{"tid":1982142,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有無動漫角色夠呢六隻pokemon 打?","createTime":"2020-04-21T05:00:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T07:18:08.000Z","uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"0010e2697166326bc11d33874c57dc387283173c","tid":1982142,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:00:10.000Z","msg":"阿爾宙斯（日文︰アルセウス，英文︰Arceus）<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.52poke.wiki/wiki/thumb/f/fc/493Arceus.png/300px-493Arceus.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.52poke.wiki%2Fwiki%2Fthumb%2Ff%2Ffc%2F493Arceus.png%2F300px-493Arceus.png&h=a3afcb3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n從虛無之地的蛋中誕生，之後創造了世界。*     神話裡描述牠是在宇宙還不存在時就誕生的最早的寶可夢。<br />\n<br />\n帝牙盧卡（日文︰ディアルガ，英文︰Dialga）<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.52poke.wiki/wiki/thumb/8/8a/483Dialga.png/300px-483Dialga.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.52poke.wiki%2Fwiki%2Fthumb%2F8%2F8a%2F483Dialga.png%2F300px-483Dialga.png&h=b4b027a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n帝牙盧卡有著控制時間的能力，被稱作時間之神。牠可以扭曲時間以讓時間加快或減慢甚至停止。<br />\n<br />\n帕路奇亞（日文︰パルキア，英文︰Palkia）<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.52poke.wiki/wiki/thumb/6/66/484Palkia.png/300px-484Palkia.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.52poke.wiki%2Fwiki%2Fthumb%2F6%2F66%2F484Palkia.png%2F300px-484Palkia.png&h=d9b39c8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n帕路奇亞具有扭曲空間並創造平行空間的能力。<br />\n<br />\n萊希拉姆（日文︰レシラム，英文︰Reshiram）<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.52poke.wiki/wiki/thumb/8/8d/643Reshiram.png/300px-643Reshiram.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.52poke.wiki%2Fwiki%2Fthumb%2F8%2F8d%2F643Reshiram.png%2F300px-643Reshiram.png&h=35b25683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n萊希拉姆是唯一能學會交錯火焰和青焰的寶可夢，當力量爆發時，尾部會呈紅色，並不時爆出火焰；集中力量時甚至能使出能將世界燃燒殆盡的招式。會幫助構築真實世界的人。<br />\n<br />\n捷克羅姆（日文︰ゼクロム，英文︰Zekrom）<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.52poke.wiki/wiki/thumb/8/81/644Zekrom.png/300px-644Zekrom.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.52poke.wiki%2Fwiki%2Fthumb%2F8%2F81%2F644Zekrom.png%2F300px-644Zekrom.png&h=b2458ec8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 能以閃電將世界燃燒殆盡的傳說的寶可夢。會輔助創造理想世界的人。<br />\n<br />\n基拉祈（日文︰ジラーチ，英文︰Jirachi）<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.52poke.wiki/wiki/thumb/8/85/385Jirachi.png/300px-385Jirachi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.52poke.wiki%2Fwiki%2Fthumb%2F8%2F85%2F385Jirachi.png%2F300px-385Jirachi.png&h=63544fe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n牠擁有可以實現任何願望的能力，許願者要讓基拉祈腹部的「真實之眼」睜開，然後看著第三隻眼許下願望。在基拉祈的頭上貼有顯示願望的「許願箋」。"},{"pid":"0ba28dbb8e50727e930f4badae769d12f1fa8d9b","tid":1982142,"uid":106604,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:04:18.000Z","msg":"我拎隻比卡超都打爆佢地啦"},{"pid":"a3e8318b432a8ae5947a829c3b4d763c60b57592","tid":1982142,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0ba28dbb8e50727e930f4badae769d12f1fa8d9b","tid":1982142,"uid":106604,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:04:18.000Z","msg":"我拎隻比卡超都打爆佢地啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ae1a0382bd2376dc19ed0297664aabdee40da2","tid":1982142,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:28:30.000Z","msg":"泰山"},{"pid":"d463984b599f14fc10d3e90298dbcf1947db6184","tid":1982142,"uid":8542,"like":32,"dislike":3,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:29:28.000Z","msg":"6隻恥鬼"},{"pid":"96cc1d47a206bf736ed9f94e231d51225e6a7b9d","tid":1982142,"uid":59570,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:29:48.000Z","msg":"令佢地中無限月讀"},{"pid":"8cc9d435f5a79e0f15ce3b29c1ac2abccb0cda19","tid":1982142,"uid":233727,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:29:49.000Z","msg":"超夢有冇份？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db96e9c216f0740dbfe5dd1296e0696ecf0e2ec","tid":1982142,"uid":47524,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,